I took it one day
at your school.

840
00:50:54,964 --> 00:50:56,923
Diana Escobebo.
Escobebo, yeah.

841
00:50:57,097 --> 00:51:00,100
I figured you were
more of a Puerto Rican
than a Marcia Brady.

842
00:51:00,274 --> 00:51:03,843
