969
01:01:21,416 --> 01:01:23,549
Slower, slow, slow.
Just like Smitty.

970
01:01:23,723 --> 01:01:25,464
There you go.

971
01:01:25,638 --> 01:01:27,422
Okay, this is it.

972
01:01:44,744 --> 01:01:46,659
[GUARD SPEAKING ARABIC]

